yle="height:3.008em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord cjk_fallback">当</span><span class="mord"> </span></span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord"> </span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">为奇数</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.19em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
